WEBVTT

00:00:30.087 --> 00:00:32.959
"Do you have a menu (Arabic)?"

00:00:33.683 --> 00:00:37.443
He looked at me strangely,
thinking that he misheard.

00:00:37.633 --> 00:00:39.706
He said, "Sorry? (English)."

00:00:40.132 --> 00:00:43.550
I said,
"The menu (Arabic), please."

00:00:44.110 --> 00:00:47.403
He replied,
"Don't you know what they call it?"

00:00:47.714 --> 00:00:49.008
"I do."

00:00:49.133 --> 00:00:52.618
He said, "No! It's called "menu" (English),
or "menu" (French)."

00:00:52.688 --> 00:00:54.613
Is the French pronunciation correct?

00:00:54.663 --> 00:00:57.053
"Come, come, take care of this one!"
said the waiter.

00:00:57.123 --> 00:01:01.358
He was disgusted when talking to me,
as if he was saying to himself,